<i>Now that I had</i>
<i>my list memorized,</i>

06:08.500 --> 06:11.500
<i>I went to the supermarket</i>
<i>to buy everything.</i>

06:11.567 --> 06:13.867
<i>But even though</i>
<i>I knew exactly what I wanted,</i>

06:13.934 --> 06:15.133
<i>I had a really hard time</i>

06:15.200 --> 06:16.900
<i>finding some things</i>
<i>in the store.</i>

