<i>would allow a robbery</i>
<i>to take place in broad daylight.</i>

06:42.266 --> 06:45.900
<i>But maybe that's not what</i>
<i>it was, uh, programmed to do.</i>

06:48.166 --> 06:50.467
<i>So I got as much as I could</i>
<i>off the list...</i>

06:50.533 --> 06:53.467
<i>but, uh, I still couldn't find</i>
<i>any Zagnut bars.</i>

06:54.633 --> 06:57.800
<i>Unfortunately,</i>
<i>this fucking machine</i>

06:57.867 --> 07:00.266
<i>could not accept questions,</i>

