-JERRY: Absolutely.
-JOHN: Yeah.

20:01.834 --> 20:02.867
Yeah.

20:07.166 --> 20:08.667
JERRY:
Not gonna lie, I'm a bachelor.

20:10.700 --> 20:12.033
JOHN: Me, too.

20:12.100 --> 20:14.000
-JERRY: Really? Very nice.
-JOHN: Yeah.

20:14.066 --> 20:16.133
JERRY: It's the way to be, man.

20:16.200 --> 20:17.567
Save a lot more money that way.

